headline: CF Industries Announces Joint Venture with JERA Co., Inc., and Mitsui & Co., Inc., for Production and Offtake of Low-Carbon Ammonia
summary: NORTHBROOK, Ill., April 08, 2025--CF Industries Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: CF), the world’s largest producer of ammonia, announced today that it has formed a joint venture with JERA Co., Inc. (JERA), Japan’s largest energy company, and Mitsui & Co., Inc. (Mitsui), a leading global investment and trading company, for the construction, production and offtake of low-carbon ammonia.
